<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Contact | GIIS Robotics Club</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="resources/favicon.ico">
    <style>
        @font-face {
            font-family: 'crest';
            src: url('/crst.otf') format('opentype');
        }
        @font-face {
            font-family: 'crestb';
            src: url('/crstb.otf') format('opentype');
        }
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        html, body {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            margin: 0;
            background-color: #111111;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-family: 'crest';
            background-image: url('/logo/background.png');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            background-attachment: fixed;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }
        nav {
            padding: 15px 20px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(20, 33, 61, 0.8) 51%, rgba(30, 30, 47, 0.8) 100%);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 0 0 20px 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 22px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
        }
        .nav-brand {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
        }
        .nav-brand span {
            font-size: 14px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            list-style: none;
            gap: 25px;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .nav-links a {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 14px;
            padding: 8px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .nav-links a:hover, .nav-links a.active {
            background: rgba(108, 99, 255, 0.2);
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        .login-link {
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 14px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6c63ff, #4a47a3);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .login-link:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #5a52d5, #3e3b8a);
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }
        .main-content {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 100px 20px 50px;
        }
        .contact-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .contact-card {
            backdrop-filter: blur(25px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(25px);
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(35,35,55,0.75), rgba(25,18,40,0.75));
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
            border-radius: 22px;
            padding: 50px 40px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6), 0 8px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .contact-card::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 85% 15%, rgba(108,99,255,0.15), transparent 60%);
            pointer-events: none;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }
        
        .contact-card > * {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .contact-logo {
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        .contact-title {
            font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 2.5rem);
            font-family: 'crestb';
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff, #e0e6ff);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }
        .contact-description {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .contact-methods {
            display: grid;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 35px;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .contact-item {
            backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            border-radius: 14px;
            padding: 20px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .contact-item:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
        }
        .contact-item-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .contact-icon {
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .contact-item h3 {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        .contact-item p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .contact-item a {
            color: #6c63ff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .contact-item a:hover {
            color: #5a52d5;
        }
        .btn-primary {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(82,108,218,1) 0%, rgba(44,75,205,1) 24%, rgba(82,108,218,1) 71%, rgba(82,108,218,1) 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-family: 'crest';
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 24px -6px rgba(66,84,214,0.35);
            border: 2px solid transparent;
        }
        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(98,122,230,1) 0%, rgba(54,85,215,1) 24%, rgba(98,122,230,1) 71%, rgba(98,122,230,1) 100%);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 14px 30px -8px rgba(66,84,214,0.4);
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .nav-links {
                display: none;
            }
            .login-link {
                font-size: 12px;
                padding: 8px 16px;
            }
            .contact-card {
                padding: 35px 25px;
            }
        }
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .main-content {
                padding: 80px 15px 40px;
            }
            .contact-card {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            nav {
                padding: 12px 15px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <a href="/" class="nav-brand">
            <img src="/logo/logo-white.png" alt="GIIS Robotics Club Logo" width="28" height="28">
            <span>GIIS Robotics Club | <%= new Date().getMonth() >= 3 ? new Date().getFullYear() : new Date().getFullYear() - 1 %> - <%= new Date().getMonth() >= 3 ? new Date().getFullYear() + 1 : new Date().getFullYear() %></span>
        </a>
        <ul class="nav-links">
            <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="/contact" class="active">Contact</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://blueprint.giisrobotics.club" target="_blank">Our Event</a></li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/login" class="login-link">Login</a>
    </nav>
    
    <div class="main-content">
        <div class="contact-container">
            <div class="contact-card">
                <div class="contact-logo">
                    <img src="/logo/logo-white.png" alt="GIIS Robotics Club Logo" width="60" height="60">
                </div>
                <h1 class="contact-title">Get in Touch</h1>
                <p class="contact-description">Ready to join our robotics community? Have questions or collaboration ideas? We'd love to hear from you!</p>
                
                <div class="contact-methods">
                    <div class="contact-item">
                        <div class="contact-item-header">
                            <h3>Email</h3>
                        </div>
                        <p>Drop us a line for inquiries, partnerships, or general questions.</p>
                        <a href="mailto:giisrobotics@gmail.com">giisrobotics@gmail.com</a>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="contact-item">
                        <div class="contact-item-header">
                            <h3>Social Media</h3>
                        </div>
                        <p>Follow us for updates, project showcases, and behind-the-scenes content.</p>
                        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/giis.roboticsclub/" target="_blank">@giis.roboticsclub</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <a href="https://www.instagram.com/giis.roboticsclub/" target="_blank" class="btn-primary">Visit Our Instagram</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>